column1:
							Hi everyone~ I am new to the forum~ A 'newbie' so to speak!  From Canada~ a city called Barrie, Ontario~ about 40 minutes north of Toronto.  To echo some other in various posts~ geez~ I really wish I had found this site sooner!  BTW~ I sincerely wish you ALL well with your cancers and any treatments that you are going through.

In reply to the thread~ You all sound very interesting with exciting and fun 'hobbies'.  

What do I like to do~

~I am a bit of a computer and Internet addict  ;
~Love to travel~ Mexico has been my destination of choice lately;
~Spending time with family~ parents, brother, sister and their spouses and my two beautiful nephews;
~I read A LOT~ Anything from fiction novels, classic literature, biographies and language studies to fashion and entertainment magazines;
~LOVE movies! New and older;
~Really enjoy going out to dinner with family and friends~ particularly trying out new restaurants with exciting new menus;
~I love the outdoors and sunshine;
Enjoy crafting~ especially scrapbooking.

							Hi Martha Anne;

